HEADWORD: Orangeroot
<hw>Or"ange*root`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An American ranunculaceous plant (<spn>Hidrastis Canadensis</spn>),
having a yellow tuberous root; -- also called
<altname>yellowroot</altname>, <altname>golden seal</altname>,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

